sentences: Kim Dong-han (Korean: 김동한; born July 3, 1998), also known mononymously as Donghan, is a South Korean singer, songwriter and actor.
Kim made his solo debut with the release of his EP D-Day in June 2018.
He is currently a member of South Korean boy band WEi.
Kim was born on July 3, 1998, and was raised in Daegu, South Korea.
